Ruoxi,

25
00:02:16,340 --> 00:02:17,260
I don't care

26
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:18,700
what happened between

27
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:19,860
you and 8th Brother in the past.

28
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:23,060
