29
00:02:23,060 --> 00:02:24,900
you have to treat him well.

30
00:02:27,700 --> 00:02:29,300
How did you know?

31
00:02:30,140 --> 00:02:31,340
Does the 4th Prince know?

32
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:32,800
4th Brother doesn't know.

33
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,120
First of all, you hid it well.

34
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:37,780
Secondly, everyone thinks that there is something going on between you and 14th Brother.

35
00:02:38,740 --> 00:02:41,100
I'm only telling you because I'm a little inebriated.

36
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:44,420
Who knew, I would be actually right.

37
00:02:45,620 --> 00:02:47,360
You cannot let the 4th Prince know.

38
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,760
I promise you.

39
00:02:54,460 --> 00:02:55,580
But aren't you

40
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:57,620
thinking of 4th Brother a little too petty?

41
00:02:58,620 --> 00:03:00,360
If Zuo Ying can be tolerant toward Min Min,

42
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:03,460
why can't 4th Brother be tolerant toward you?

43
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:05,720
I've never felt

44
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:07,400
that a woman before marriage,

45
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:10,080
could not like someone else.

46
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,200
Of course, I wouldn't mind him knowing.

47
00:03:13,820 --> 00:03:16,180
If it was 10th Prince or 14th Prince

48
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:17,780
or any other person,

49
00:03:17,780 --> 00:03:19,660
I would have told him long ago.

50
00:03:20,780 --> 00:03:22,700
But I couldn't since it was 8th Prince.

51
00:03:23,580 --> 00:03:25,020
What do you mean?

52
00:03:27,020 --> 00:03:29,060
I cannot tell you.

53
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:31,220
But it's true,

54
00:03:31,780 --> 00:03:35,020
for 8th Prince's sake, I can't tell him.

55
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:37,940
Whether it's now or later

56
00:03:37,940 --> 00:03:39,660
and even if he doesn't mind it.

57
00:03:40,620 --> 00:03:42,740
But I cannot take that risk.

58
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:44,940
It's a risk

59
00:03:46,100 --> 00:03:47,800
I cannot afford.

60
00:03:54,180 --> 00:03:56,100
Though I don't understand it or why,

61
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:57,860
I trust you.

62
00:03:58,460 --> 00:04:00,900
You must have your own reasons.

63
00:04:02,060 --> 00:04:04,280
How fortunate I am

64
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:06,420
to have you as a friend.

65
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:15,860
Actually,

66
00:04:16,140 --> 00:04:18,700
4th Brother hides his thoughts very deeply.

67
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:20,540
And it's extremely hard for him to get close to anyone.

68
00:04:20,540 --> 00:04:23,139
Such people easily suffer alone.

69
00:04:23,460 --> 00:04:25,740
Although, I can help to share some of his worries,

70
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:29,260
he is still lonesome after all.

71
00:04:29,260 --> 00:04:32,460
But you are different from everybody else.

72
00:04:33,180 --> 00:04:35,020
Although, you aren't highly educated,

73
00:04:35,020 --> 00:04:36,300
I've always felt

74
00:04:36,820 --> 00:04:38,660
you're not any less well-read than us.

75
00:04:38,660 --> 00:04:41,480
You've even studied things that we haven't.

76
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:44,580
Ruoxi, as long as you are willing,

77
00:04:44,580 --> 00:04:47,260
you really can open 4th Brother's heart.

78
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:48,900
And only you can

79
00:04:49,700 --> 00:04:52,060
because you can understand his ambition

80
00:04:52,060 --> 00:04:53,680
and also understand his pain.

81
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:56,974
There are a few other things

82
00:04:57,267 --> 00:04:59,614
I might as well simply tell you today.

83
00:04:59,614 --> 00:05:01,628
Otherwise, I don't know when

84
00:05:01,628 --> 00:05:03,900
I will get a chance to in future.

85
00:05:04,349 --> 00:05:05,674
You have to remember this well,

86
00:05:07,089 --> 00:05:08,503
now that you're in the palace,

87
00:05:08,503 --> 00:05:10,129
all that you have

88
00:05:10,129 --> 00:05:12,700
comes from receiving Imperial Father's favors.

89
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:14,271
Imperial Father trusts you

90
00:05:14,271 --> 00:05:16,240
because you don't have any hidden agendas.

91
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,723
You don't take anyone's side

92
00:05:17,723 --> 00:05:19,534
or suppress anyone.

93
00:05:19,534 --> 00:05:22,035
You just wholeheartedly serve Imperial Father.

94
00:05:22,540 --> 00:05:23,620
But,

95
00:05:25,260 --> 00:05:26,506
if you get involved

96
00:05:26,506 --> 00:05:28,126
in our brothers' feud,

97
00:05:28,126 --> 00:05:30,030
you will lose everything you have.

98
00:05:30,726 --> 00:05:34,200
Ruoxi, in this deep palace,

99
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:37,167
the ending result will be too dreadful to ponder.

100
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:40,711
This has always been a fight amongst us men.

101
00:05:40,711 --> 00:05:42,011
We do this

102
00:05:42,011 --> 00:05:44,040
to obtain more wishes,

103
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,500
secret desires,

104
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:47,584
and even more rank and honor.

105
00:05:47,584 --> 00:05:50,171
To be able to sit in the highest position,

106
00:05:50,951 --> 00:05:52,569
regardless of the results,

107
00:05:52,569 --> 00:05:53,420
this is all that we

108
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:55,438
knowingly accept.

109
00:05:55,438 --> 00:05:56,767
But you? Why do you

110
00:05:56,767 --> 00:05:59,428
make sacrifices for our personal battles?

111
00:06:00,587 --> 00:06:03,745
They should not be your sacrifices.

112
00:06:04,860 --> 00:06:07,168
Why suddenly tell me all this?

113
00:06:07,437 --> 00:06:09,680
Because 8th Brother is your brother-in-law.

114
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:12,660
Let alone, you and him...

115
00:06:13,900 --> 00:06:15,857
as well as 10th Brother and 14th Brother

116
00:06:15,857 --> 00:06:17,972
are people whom you cannot part with.

117
00:06:17,972 --> 00:06:20,180
But since you promised 4th Brother that

118
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:21,857
you will be 4th Brother's woman,

119
00:06:21,857 --> 00:06:23,225
I'm afraid that in a moment of haste

120
00:06:23,225 --> 00:06:24,860
you will get involved in our struggles.

121
00:06:24,860 --> 00:06:26,420
I know

122
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:27,994
watching everything that's happening

123
00:06:27,994 --> 00:06:29,566
will make you suffer.

124
00:06:29,566 --> 00:06:31,089
But if you get involved,

125
00:06:31,089 --> 00:06:33,142
you will suffer even more.

126
00:06:39,434 --> 00:06:41,385
This is the royal family,

127
00:06:41,919 --> 00:06:44,140
where it's impossible to avoid feuding and suffering.

128
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:46,424
No one can stop it.

129
00:06:46,424 --> 00:06:48,467
Even wise and farsighted Imperial Father

130
00:06:48,467 --> 00:06:49,420
can only helplessly

131
00:06:49,420 --> 00:06:51,478
watch events unfold.

132
00:06:51,980 --> 00:06:53,390
Not to mention you.

133
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:58,577
Ruoxi,

134
00:06:59,775 --> 00:07:02,469
I just want you to follow 4th Brother safely

135
00:07:02,469 --> 00:07:04,108
and treat him well.

136
00:07:04,108 --> 00:07:06,773
Everything else is secondary.

137
00:07:07,438 --> 00:07:09,142
Whoever wins and whoever loses,

138
00:07:09,992 --> 00:07:12,467
is between the rest of us.

139
00:07:22,420 --> 00:07:23,908
Didn't we agree

140
00:07:23,924 --> 00:07:25,683
to get drunk tonight?

141
00:07:28,707 --> 00:07:32,471
