142
00:07:56,223 --> 00:07:58,252
Jie'jie, you're awake.

143
00:07:59,060 --> 00:08:00,540
Yu Tan,

144
00:08:00,540 --> 00:08:02,051
when you came back last night

145
00:08:02,051 --> 00:08:03,637
