149
00:08:11,453 --> 00:08:13,197
No need. I'll go right away.

150
00:08:13,691 --> 00:08:15,038
Slow down!

151
00:08:20,139 --> 00:08:21,532
Ruoxi Jie`jie.

152
00:08:21,580 --> 00:08:22,693
Ruoxi Jie`jie.

153
00:08:22,693 --> 00:08:23,978
His Majesty is holding court

154
00:08:23,978 --> 00:08:24,906
