155
00:08:24,906 --> 00:08:26,385
Jie'jie, you need to be careful.

156
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,561
Alright.

157
00:08:50,540 --> 00:08:52,174
I have already ordered,

158
00:08:52,174 --> 00:08:53,242
that if among any of you princes

159
00:08:53,242 --> 00:08:55,682
anyone schemes against the Crown Prince,

160
00:08:55,682 --> 00:08:58,884
he is a traitor to the country and has committed a crime!

161
00:08:58,884 --> 00:09:01,471
Did you order someone, through various means of communication,

162
00:09:01,471 --> 00:09:03,600
to spread rumors and slander

163
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:06,895
loudly about the Crown Prince's actions

164
00:09:06,895 --> 00:09:09,900
to the Manchurian officials in the capital city

165
00:09:09,900 --> 00:09:11,671
and the citizens of Jiangnan province?

166
00:09:11,671 --> 00:09:14,172
Thus, making it seem as if the Crown Prince's public image

167
00:09:14,172 --> 00:09:17,005
might raise questions about his succession to the throne and

168
00:09:17,005 --> 00:09:19,838
that at anytime he might lose his position.

169
00:09:19,838 --> 00:09:22,600
How conniving and devious, Yong Qinwang!
(Yong - his name, Qinwang - princely rank )

170
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,171
Respectfully, Imperial Father,

171
00:09:24,260 --> 00:09:27,175
this was not my doing.

172
00:09:27,175 --> 00:09:29,172
- Your subject is guilty.
- Your subject is guilty.

173
00:09:29,172 --> 00:09:32,144
This matter definitely has nothing to do with 4th Prince

174
00:09:32,144 --> 00:09:35,302
It is all our doing.

175
00:09:35,302 --> 00:09:39,017
You two are loyal for sure,

176
00:09:39,017 --> 00:09:41,943
but do you still see me as your king?

177
00:09:46,380 --> 00:09:47,609
For the past two to three years,

178
00:09:47,609 --> 00:09:51,417
you both have been secretly dealing with 4th Prince.

179
00:09:51,417 --> 00:09:54,203
Where and with what people,

180
00:09:54,203 --> 00:09:56,154
all that evidence has been recorded.

181
00:09:56,154 --> 00:09:57,872
If they weren't doing all this for you,

182
00:09:57,872 --> 00:10:01,587
don't tell me, it was they themselves that coveted the Crown Prince's status.

183
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:06,856
Even though I have conversed with them before,

184
00:10:06,856 --> 00:10:09,746
I have never instructed them to do any such thing.

185
00:10:10,016 --> 00:10:11,767
I hope it's not 4th Brother,

186
00:10:11,767 --> 00:10:13,935
otherwise, you two will only suffer along with him

187
00:10:15,124 --> 00:10:16,703
and all my efforts

188
00:10:16,703 --> 00:10:19,351
in helping you out, would be in vain.

189
00:10:19,860 --> 00:10:21,998
He was the one who set up 4th Prince,

190
00:10:21,998 --> 00:10:23,530
killing two birds with one stone,

191
00:10:23,530 --> 00:10:26,220
by striking a blow at the Crown Prince and also getting rid of 4th Prince.

192
00:10:26,220 --> 00:10:27,779
E'ling'e and Kui'xu

193
00:10:27,779 --> 00:10:29,544
were the ones who spread rumors everywhere.

194
00:10:29,544 --> 00:10:31,541
On the surface, they appear to be shielding 4th Prince,

195
00:10:31,541 --> 00:10:34,095
but in actual fact, they were carrying out 8th Prince's orders

196
00:10:34,095 --> 00:10:35,540
to frame 4th Prince.

197
00:10:35,540 --> 00:10:38,043
He really thought through this plan very carefully and methodically.

198
00:10:38,940 --> 00:10:41,270
I only know that the Crown prince will be stripped of his title this year.

199
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:44,010
But what about 4th Prince?

200
00:10:47,841 --> 00:10:49,513
13th Prince...

201
00:10:50,767 --> 00:10:52,485
13th Brother...

202
00:10:55,411 --> 00:10:57,088
Since things have come to this stage

203
00:10:57,088 --> 00:10:59,514
Imperial Father will find out the truth sooner or later,

204
00:10:59,514 --> 00:11:01,379
so I will make my confession now.

205
00:11:01,820 --> 00:11:05,581
This matter was my doing. I secretly incited E'ling'e and Kui'xu.

206
00:11:05,581 --> 00:11:06,728
Under the pretext of using 4th Brother's name

207
00:11:06,728 --> 00:11:08,854
I ordered them to spread rumors everywhere.

208
00:11:08,854 --> 00:11:11,015
Since everything has been exposed today,

209
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:13,894
then no one should think of shedding responsibility.

210
00:11:13,894 --> 00:11:15,148
13th Brother,

211
00:11:15,148 --> 00:11:17,122
your words are really strange.

212
00:11:17,122 --> 00:11:18,536
Everyone knows that you and 4th Brother

213
00:11:18,536 --> 00:11:20,180
are inseparable companions.

214
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:23,291
Your intentions are as good as saying they're 4th Brother's intentions?

215
00:11:23,291 --> 00:11:25,451
Imperial Father, just ask E'ling'e and Kui'xu

216
00:11:25,451 --> 00:11:26,821
whether I'm the one who instructed them in this matter.

217
00:11:26,821 --> 00:11:28,453
You'll have the answer immediately.

218
00:11:30,004 --> 00:11:32,540
What is the truth of this matter?

219
00:11:32,829 --> 00:11:35,287
The...

220
00:11:35,287 --> 00:11:36,912
Imperial Father.

221
00:11:38,602 --> 00:11:39,810
In my opinion,

222
00:11:39,810 --> 00:11:41,806
this matter is not something 4th Brother would do.

223
00:11:41,806 --> 00:11:43,485
4th Brother is like a hermit.

224
00:11:43,485 --> 00:11:45,197
He often meditates and recites scriptures in his residence.

225
00:11:45,197 --> 00:11:46,636
He is usually is the most filial.

226
00:11:46,636 --> 00:11:48,401
He is always considerate of Imperial Father's regard.

227
00:11:48,401 --> 00:11:50,723
He definitely wouldn't do something so immoral.

228
00:11:50,723 --> 00:11:53,106
I deserve death.

229
00:11:53,106 --> 00:11:54,763
What 13th Prince has said is the truth.

230
00:11:54,763 --> 00:11:56,621
Y-Yes, it was 13th Prince.

231
00:11:56,621 --> 00:11:57,410
This year

232
00:11:57,410 --> 00:11:59,073
on the eighth day of the third month,

233
00:11:59,073 --> 00:12:01,216
there was a secret meeting at Qu'hua'lou,

234
00:12:01,216 --> 00:12:03,738
where he gave us the instructions.

235
00:12:03,738 --> 00:12:05,769
We were to spread rumors about all of the Crown Prince's transgressions

236
00:12:05,769 --> 00:12:07,441
Those were his orders.

237
00:12:07,441 --> 00:12:09,313
I wouldn't dare to deceive your Imperial Majesty.

238
00:12:09,313 --> 00:12:10,321
That's right, that's right.

239
00:12:10,321 --> 00:12:12,014
4th Prince,

240
00:12:12,148 --> 00:12:15,845
is all this really the 13th Prince's doing?

241
00:12:21,622 --> 00:12:24,090
This question is a trap.

242
00:12:24,090 --> 00:12:28,384
To answer yes or no wouldn't be right.

243
00:12:29,934 --> 00:12:32,935
This matter was not my doing.

244
00:12:35,110 --> 00:12:37,572
I also have no idea,

245
00:12:37,572 --> 00:12:40,412
if it was 13th brother's doing.

246
00:12:47,303 --> 00:12:49,275
3rd Prince.

247
00:12:49,275 --> 00:12:50,336
Yes, Imperial Father.

248
00:12:50,336 --> 00:12:51,629
13th Prince is to be

249
00:12:51,629 --> 00:12:53,951
placed under house arrest at Yang'feng'jia'dao.

250
00:12:53,951 --> 00:12:55,251
Without my permission,

251
00:12:55,251 --> 00:12:57,991
no one is allowed to visit him.

252
00:12:57,991 --> 00:13:00,267
With regards to E'ling'e and Kui'xu,

253
00:13:00,267 --> 00:13:04,168
they will be handed over to the Ministry of Justice for investigation and punishment.

254
00:13:04,168 --> 00:13:05,582
Yes.

255
00:13:28,363 --> 00:13:33,585
I obey your decree and offer my gratitude.

256
00:13:40,809 --> 00:13:46,496
13th prince, from today onward, we will be separated.

257
00:13:57,845 --> 00:13:58,967
Court is dismissed.

258
00:13:58,967 --> 00:14:02,843
Court is dismissed.

259
00:15:40,338 --> 00:15:42,781
Go back.

260
00:15:52,505 --> 00:15:59,314
For the sake of 13th Prince, please go back.

261
00:17:00,911 --> 00:17:05,537
4th Prince has not entered the palace for many days.

262
00:17:14,006 --> 00:17:15,066
Greetings to Li Gong Gong.

263
00:17:15,066 --> 00:17:16,799
No need.

264
00:17:16,799 --> 00:17:17,877
13th Prince has been

265
00:17:17,877 --> 00:17:20,559
exiled for seven days already.

266
00:17:20,559 --> 00:17:23,360
4th Prince is quietly reflecting at home

267
00:17:23,360 --> 00:17:26,109
and avoiding all politics.

268
00:17:26,109 --> 00:17:28,300
I'm afraid that during this time,

269
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:30,547
he won't be entering the palace.

270
00:17:30,547 --> 00:17:31,920
Because of this matter, the Emperor

271
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:34,516
is extremely sad.

272
00:17:35,804 --> 00:17:37,780
As the person serving at the Emperor's side,

273
00:17:37,780 --> 00:17:39,712
you should be aware of the appropriate behavior.

274
00:17:39,712 --> 00:17:42,219
Things that should not be said, should not be spoken.

275
00:17:42,219 --> 00:17:44,584
Unwelcomed sympathy,

276
00:17:44,584 --> 00:17:46,140
should just be felt in your heart.

277
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:49,007
By all means, avoid trouble.

278
00:17:49,007 --> 00:17:50,880
Much thanks, Li'gong'gong for your reminders.

279
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:52,450
You're are an intelligent person.

280
00:17:52,450 --> 00:17:56,500
I don't need to say too much.

281
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:59,400
Li'gong'gong.

282
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,806
Jie'jie.

283
00:18:03,420 --> 00:18:05,220
What's wrong?

284
00:18:07,980 --> 00:18:11,344
Nothing much, just feeling a little dizzy.

285
00:18:11,344 --> 00:18:13,160
Are you falling sick?

286
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:16,020
Why don't you go back and rest for awhile?

287
00:18:16,885 --> 00:18:19,280
Please handle my duties, then.

288
00:18:43,200 --> 00:18:44,224
Little brother,

289
00:18:44,224 --> 00:18:46,340
I beg of you, please help me pass a message to 4th Prince.

290
00:18:46,340 --> 00:18:48,062
Lu'wu has an important matter to discuss with him.

291
00:18:48,062 --> 00:18:49,080
4th Prince has stated that he won't be entertaining visitors.

292
00:18:49,080 --> 00:18:51,380
He won't meet with anyone.

293
00:18:51,820 --> 00:18:53,700
If 4th Prince refuses to see me today,

294
00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:55,720
I will continue to kneel down here.

295
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,799
If after a long while, 4th Prince still refuses to see me,

296
00:18:57,799 --> 00:19:00,900
I will be kneeling here for a very long time.

297
00:19:00,900 --> 00:19:02,340
Suit yourself.

298
00:19:25,740 --> 00:19:27,660
Wang'ye.

299
00:19:31,380 --> 00:19:35,013
I understand what Wang'ye is going through now.

300
00:19:35,013 --> 00:19:36,460
13th Brother has accompanied you

301
00:19:36,460 --> 00:19:37,700
for so many years.

302
00:19:37,700 --> 00:19:39,480
Today, he took the blame from you.

303
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,760
He must know

304
00:19:40,760 --> 00:19:43,860
you're suffering and how helpless you are.

305
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:48,280
13th Brother knows me and trusts me.

306
00:19:48,780 --> 00:19:51,620
And yet he has fallen into this state.

307
00:19:59,060 --> 00:20:02,400
Wang'ye, I believe

308
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:05,320
you definitely won't let 13th Brother continue suffering.

309
00:20:05,320 --> 00:20:08,380
You'll definitely be able to save 13th Brother.

310
00:20:15,709 --> 00:20:18,452
Wang ye.

311
00:20:18,452 --> 00:20:19,717
Wang'ye.

312
00:20:19,717 --> 00:20:23,000
Why are you so flustered? Have you forgotten our house rules?

313
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:25,766
I know my mistake now, please forgive me.

314
00:20:25,766 --> 00:20:27,813
Forget it. Stand up and speak.

315
00:20:29,037 --> 00:20:30,420
There's a woman outside...

316
00:20:30,420 --> 00:20:32,981
asking to see you. She said she's Lu'wu.

317
00:20:32,981 --> 00:20:36,080
I told her that you won't see anyone...

318
00:20:36,080 --> 00:20:40,397
but she said she will kneel outside until you see her.

319
00:20:40,397 --> 00:20:42,620
She's really a love-sick fool.

320
00:20:43,551 --> 00:20:44,555
But for now,

321
00:20:44,555 --> 00:20:46,273
even if I could think of some ideas

322
00:20:46,273 --> 00:20:48,681
I wouldn't be able to do anything.

323
00:20:49,881 --> 00:20:51,607
Give her my reply.

324
00:20:51,607 --> 00:20:53,279
Tell her

325
00:20:53,279 --> 00:20:54,604
kneeling down outside my residence

326
00:20:54,604 --> 00:20:56,529
will only be wasting her time,

327
00:20:56,529 --> 00:20:57,862
so let her leave early.

328
00:20:57,862 --> 00:20:59,130
Yes.

329
00:21:15,123 --> 00:21:16,518
Hurry up and leave. Wang'ye said

330
00:21:16,518 --> 00:21:18,404
you are only wasting your time.

331
00:21:18,404 --> 00:21:19,472
It's of no use.

332
00:21:19,472 --> 00:21:20,920
Hurry and leave.

333
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:23,791
Leave. Hurry and leave.

334
00:21:23,791 --> 00:21:26,692
4th Prince really said that?

335
00:22:01,540 --> 00:22:03,054
13th Prince.

336
00:22:03,398 --> 00:22:05,140
From today on,

337
00:22:05,140 --> 00:22:07,538
who will drink wine with you?

338
00:22:07,538 --> 00:22:09,535
Listen to you playing the flute

339
00:22:09,535 --> 00:22:12,342
and have heart-to-heart talks on all matters?

340
00:22:20,998 --> 00:22:22,327
Ruoxi.

341
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:34,801
Since you're here, why didn't you answer me?

342
00:22:35,959 --> 00:22:37,327
So you really are planning

343
00:22:37,327 --> 00:22:39,278
that from now on, besides a greeting,

344
00:22:39,278 --> 00:22:41,553
you aren't going to talk to us.

345
00:22:43,622 --> 00:22:46,126
Can I drink some wine?

346
00:22:46,126 --> 00:22:47,653
You are a prince.

347
00:22:47,653 --> 00:22:50,539
If you want to drink, who can stop you?

348
00:23:02,181 --> 00:23:03,535
Ruoxi.

349
00:23:03,535 --> 00:23:05,997
I know you and 13th Prince are good friends.

350
00:23:05,997 --> 00:23:06,886
But we are also

351
00:23:06,886 --> 00:23:08,769
friends since we were young.

352
00:23:08,769 --> 00:23:10,719
How can you favor one and discriminate against the others?

353
00:23:11,135 --> 00:23:12,338
And also

354
00:23:12,338 --> 00:23:14,581
many things depend on one's standpoint,

355
00:23:14,581 --> 00:23:16,553
there's no right or wrong.

356
00:23:19,968 --> 00:23:22,158
Are you here to rebuke me today?

357
00:23:22,158 --> 00:23:24,640
I don't have the mood to listen.

358
00:23:33,189 --> 00:23:36,097
This is Lu'wu's letter for you.

359
00:23:40,069 --> 00:23:41,741
To see me, Lu'wu,

360
00:23:41,741 --> 00:23:42,900
in front of my door,

361
00:23:42,900 --> 00:23:44,310
knelt for one day and one night,

362
00:23:44,310 --> 00:23:46,401
before she begged a servant to help her pass on a message.

363
00:23:46,401 --> 00:23:47,544
I heard that Lu'wu,

364
00:23:47,544 --> 00:23:49,873
also knelt in front of 4th Prince's door,

365
00:23:49,873 --> 00:23:51,842
but no one bothered about her.

366
00:23:51,842 --> 00:23:54,657
Because of a lack of a better option, she came to find me.

367
00:23:59,040 --> 00:24:01,283
Lu'wu wants to take care of 13th Prince.

368
00:24:01,283 --> 00:24:03,812
Do you think it's possible?

369
00:24:03,812 --> 00:24:04,968
If you are going to reply,

370
00:24:04,968 --> 00:24:06,160
then hurry up and write it.

371
00:24:06,160 --> 00:24:08,185
I will take the letter to her when I go out.

372
00:24:08,185 --> 00:24:10,996
So as to cure her of her sentimentalism as soon as possible.

373
00:24:11,772 --> 00:24:14,187
How do you know the contents of the letter?

374
00:24:14,187 --> 00:24:16,130
Lu'wu begged me as well,

375
00:24:16,130 --> 00:24:17,802
but the Emperor has already said

376
00:24:17,802 --> 00:24:18,923
that without an Imperial Edict

377
00:24:18,923 --> 00:24:21,617
nobody can visit him.

378
00:24:21,617 --> 00:24:22,560
Originally, I didn't want to

379
00:24:22,560 --> 00:24:23,846
help her deliver this letter,

380
00:24:23,846 --> 00:24:26,580
but I felt pity for her painstaking effort.

381
00:24:26,580 --> 00:24:28,722
I thought of the friendship between you and 13th Brother.

382
00:24:28,722 --> 00:24:29,780
Maybe, your words

383
00:24:29,780 --> 00:24:31,493
can persuade her.

384
00:24:31,493 --> 00:24:33,868
Please do your best to advise her.

385
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:37,026
Lu'wu is looking extremely haggard these days.

386
00:24:37,026 --> 00:24:38,798
Even if I had a heart of stone,

387
00:24:38,798 --> 00:24:41,860
I also cannot bear to see her like this.

388
00:24:41,860 --> 00:24:43,580
So you really don't have any ideas?

389
00:24:43,580 --> 00:24:46,416
Ruoxi, if I could fulfill her wish,

390
00:24:46,416 --> 00:24:48,673
I would happily help her.

391
00:24:48,673 --> 00:24:49,958
Don't tell me that in your heart,

392
00:24:49,958 --> 00:24:51,940
I'm that cold-blooded.

393
00:24:51,940 --> 00:24:53,200
Nothing can be done, because Imperial Father

394
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:55,800
has already made a decree.

395
00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:56,820
Nowadays,

396
00:24:56,820 --> 00:24:58,962
if I have anything to do with 13th Brother

397
00:24:58,962 --> 00:24:59,820
Imperial Father will have suspicions about me

398
00:24:59,820 --> 00:25:01,580
being connected to the "spreading of rumors" matter.

399
00:25:01,580 --> 00:25:04,300
That the matter was not the will of 13th Brother alone,

400
00:25:04,300 --> 00:25:05,420
even has 4th Brother scrambling to

401
00:25:05,420 --> 00:25:07,140
cut ties with 13th Brother.

402
00:25:07,140 --> 00:25:09,209
Much less us,

403
00:25:09,209 --> 00:25:11,199
but for now, no one

404
00:25:11,199 --> 00:25:14,060
dares to speak up for 13th Brother.

405
00:25:14,060 --> 00:25:15,700
All this was originally the doing of your faction,

406
00:25:15,700 --> 00:25:17,480
so of course, you all must behave more cautiously.

407
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:19,600
If you are scolding me in your heart, go ahead and say it aloud.

408
00:25:19,600 --> 00:25:21,660
This letter, are you going to reply to it or not?

409
00:25:30,100 --> 00:25:32,940
[ Lu'wu, this person is lowly and has no power. ]

410
00:25:32,940 --> 00:25:34,480
[ Although I have no hope of any results, ]

411
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:36,100
[ I will still do my best. ]

412
00:25:36,100 --> 00:25:38,520
[ Please wait for my news. ]

413
00:25:41,903 --> 00:25:43,580
[ Take good care of yourself, ]

414
00:25:43,580 --> 00:25:45,518
[ if not, you will have no strength ]

415
00:25:45,518 --> 00:25:48,720
[ and then be unable to take care of 13th Prince. ]

416
00:26:03,080 --> 00:26:04,520
For it to be sealed this tight,

417
00:26:04,520 --> 00:26:06,540
are you scared I'm going to secretly look at it?

418
00:26:06,540 --> 00:26:08,260
It's written for Lu'wu

419
00:26:08,260 --> 00:26:09,840
and it is all girl-to-girl talk.

420
00:26:09,840 --> 00:26:12,560
I didn't want Lu'wu to feel embarrassed.

421
00:26:14,180 --> 00:26:15,680
14th Prince...

422
00:26:16,460 --> 00:26:18,360
Please inform your doorkeeper

423
00:26:18,360 --> 00:26:21,020
that when he sees Lu'wu, to behave in a courteous manner.

424
00:26:21,020 --> 00:26:23,620
Don't worry, I've already done so.

425
00:26:23,620 --> 00:26:25,180
To see her or not is up to me,

426
00:26:25,180 --> 00:26:27,300
but I won't allow him to be negligent.

427
00:26:27,300 --> 00:26:28,720
Thank you very much.

428
00:26:28,720 --> 00:26:30,740
Ruoxi, there are some things

429
00:26:30,740 --> 00:26:32,300
I know I shouldn't say, but--

430
00:26:32,300 --> 00:26:34,600
Then don't say them.

431
00:26:43,420 --> 00:26:45,300
Whether the feelings between you and 4th Brother are real

432
00:26:45,300 --> 00:26:46,660
or pretend,

433
00:26:46,660 --> 00:26:48,400
it should end here.

434
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:50,640
You are an intelligent person.

435
00:26:50,640 --> 00:26:53,200
Don't make things hard for yourself unnecessarily.

436
00:27:03,220 --> 00:27:05,840
Su'ma'la'gu's favorite season is Autumn.

437
00:27:05,840 --> 00:27:06,460
She said

438
00:27:06,460 --> 00:27:08,760
that it is more splendid than Spring.

439
00:27:08,760 --> 00:27:10,020
I also remembered

440
00:27:10,020 --> 00:27:11,260
Gu'gu standing under the yellow

441
00:27:11,260 --> 00:27:13,580
maidenhair tree, smiling and singing songs.

442
00:27:13,580 --> 00:27:15,560
The songs she can sing are a lot.

443
00:27:15,560 --> 00:27:16,540
On the grasslands,

444
00:27:16,540 --> 00:27:18,380
the best singer

445
00:27:18,380 --> 00:27:19,300
is not as good as her.

446
00:27:19,300 --> 00:27:20,080
Yes.

447
00:27:21,360 --> 00:27:22,620
Emperor,

448
00:27:22,620 --> 00:27:23,560
shall I

449
00:27:23,560 --> 00:27:25,340
tell you a story to relieve your boredom?

450
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:26,620
Fine.

451
00:27:26,620 --> 00:27:29,660
If it is a good story, I will reward you.

452
00:27:29,660 --> 00:27:30,980
In the Western Jin dynasty,

453
00:27:30,980 --> 00:27:32,740
there was a lady named Lu'zhu.

454
00:27:32,740 --> 00:27:35,580
She was a wealthy and famous courtesan.

455
00:27:35,580 --> 00:27:38,640
This story I've already heard before.

456
00:27:39,920 --> 00:27:42,200
There was a lady named Lin'si'niang.

457
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:44,180
She was originally a singer from Qin'huai.

458
00:27:44,180 --> 00:27:45,280
Later on she became Emperor Qin's

459
00:27:45,280 --> 00:27:46,600
favorite and pampered concubine.

460
00:27:46,600 --> 00:27:48,260
This, I have also heard of.

461
00:27:48,260 --> 00:27:50,160
Change it.

462
00:27:50,160 --> 00:27:52,360
Emperor, these girls,

463
00:27:52,360 --> 00:27:54,300
although they may have had a lowly background,

464
00:27:54,300 --> 00:27:55,940
they were chivalrous and full of righteousness.

465
00:27:55,940 --> 00:27:57,340
To repay their benefactor's favor and kindness,

466
00:27:57,340 --> 00:27:59,220
they sacrificed their lives.

467
00:27:59,220 --> 00:28:02,480
Shouldn't they be considered worthy of respect?

468
00:28:04,040 --> 00:28:06,340
They can be considered as outstanding women

469
00:28:06,340 --> 00:28:10,600
that surpass many men in this world.

470
00:28:10,600 --> 00:28:12,040
Emperor,

471
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:16,980
what if there is

472
00:28:16,980 --> 00:28:18,340
an  outstanding lady willing to repay her benefactor who kindly protected her,

473
00:28:18,340 --> 00:28:20,200
even if that meant she would be sacrificed?

474
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,017
That person is

475
00:28:21,017 --> 00:28:23,140
the close female friend of 13th Prince.

476
00:28:23,140 --> 00:28:24,860
Her name is Lu Wu.

477
00:28:24,860 --> 00:28:26,100
In the capital city, Lu Wu is

478
00:28:26,100 --> 00:28:27,380
a famous cultured harlot.

479
00:28:27,380 --> 00:28:29,180
I have seen her previously.

480
00:28:29,180 --> 00:28:30,380
A pitiful life,

481
00:28:30,380 --> 00:28:32,140
but she has a open-minded personality.

482
00:28:32,140 --> 00:28:33,160
Her inherent quality

483
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,920
is self-value and self-respect.

484
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,420
Her relationship with 13th Prince was not to use his position

485
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:38,460
to seek any connection.

486
00:28:38,460 --> 00:28:40,680
Now that she has heard that 13th Prince is placed under house arrest,

487
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:41,700
she through other people,

488
00:28:41,700 --> 00:28:43,620
sent a letter to Ruoxi.

489
00:28:43,620 --> 00:28:46,420
Every word of hers is filled with tears and every sentence with real emotion.

490
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:48,600
All she asks for is to suffer together with 13th Prince

491
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:49,860
and to take care of his daily needs.

492
00:28:49,860 --> 00:28:51,420
Ruoxi,

493
00:28:51,420 --> 00:28:54,860
you are relying on my favor to you.

494
00:28:54,860 --> 00:28:57,020
You dare to say anything,

495
00:28:57,020 --> 00:28:59,740
you dare to do anything.

496
00:28:59,740 --> 00:29:00,540
Li'de'quan.

497
00:29:00,540 --> 00:29:01,540
Emperor?

498
00:29:01,540 --> 00:29:02,300
Let's go back to the palace.

499
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:03,360
Yes.

500
00:29:03,360 --> 00:29:04,500
Emperor,

501
00:29:04,500 --> 00:29:05,960
you are a noble man,

502
00:29:05,960 --> 00:29:07,960
please grant Luwu's wish.

503
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:10,080
Your servant is willing to withstand any punishment.

504
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:16,160
Is it her wish or your wish?!

505
00:29:17,020 --> 00:29:18,540
Punish you?

506
00:29:18,540 --> 00:29:23,000
You couldn't handle my punishment!

507
00:29:29,940 --> 00:29:32,200
So all of that was useless.

508
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:35,031
Lu'wu,

509
00:29:35,031 --> 00:29:37,760
Ruoxi has failed you.

510
00:29:39,100 --> 00:29:40,800
How is Ruoxi?

511
00:29:40,800 --> 00:29:42,460
Responding to the Emperor,

512
00:29:42,460 --> 00:29:45,180
Ruoxi is still bowing in the garden.

513
00:29:45,180 --> 00:29:47,840
She is stubborn.

514
00:29:47,840 --> 00:29:51,040
No wonder she is called the Death-Seeking 13th Sister.

515
00:29:52,540 --> 00:29:54,780
If she wants to bow, let her.

516
00:30:13,140 --> 00:30:14,260
My good sister,

517
00:30:14,260 --> 00:30:15,900
how can you be so addled?

518
00:30:15,900 --> 00:30:18,080
Nobody dares to mention 13th Brother's situation,

519
00:30:18,080 --> 00:30:19,640
how could you?

520
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:23,740
My Master said

521
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:25,020
he will find the opportunity

522
00:30:25,020 --> 00:30:27,200
to help Jie'jie ask for forgiveness,

523
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:29,840
just endure for a little longer.

524
00:30:35,260 --> 00:30:36,440
At this time, Lu'Wu

525
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:38,680
is probably crying inwardly.

526
00:30:39,040 --> 00:30:41,040
The lonely 13th Prince

527
00:30:41,040 --> 00:30:42,760
probably can only look up

528
00:30:42,760 --> 00:30:45,260
since only stars are his companions.

529
00:30:45,260 --> 00:30:50,520
His flute may sound but no one is there to comfort him.

530
00:31:06,100 --> 00:31:07,840
Drink.

531
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:10,356
Drink!

532
00:31:43,340 --> 00:31:44,680
Wang'ye.

533
00:31:45,320 --> 00:31:46,940
What?

534
00:31:47,740 --> 00:31:49,200
News from the palace.

535
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,320
Today, in the afternoon,

536
00:31:50,320 --> 00:31:52,060
Miss Ruoxi, for 13th Prince's problem,

537
00:31:52,060 --> 00:31:53,480
contradicted the Emperor.

538
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:57,144
Now she is kneeling in the garden as a punishment.

